org.foxlabs.validation.constraint

Class PropertyComparisonConstraint<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.foxlabs.validation.AbstractValidation<V>
      • org.foxlabs.validation.constraint.CheckConstraint<V>
        • org.foxlabs.validation.constraint.PropertyComparisonConstraint<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - The type of operands
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Constraint<V>, Validation<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PropertyComparisonConstraint.EqualToOp, PropertyComparisonConstraint.GreaterThanEqualOp, PropertyComparisonConstraint.GreaterThanOp, PropertyComparisonConstraint.LessThanEqualOp, PropertyComparisonConstraint.LessThanOp, PropertyComparisonConstraint.NotEqualToOp

    public abstract class PropertyComparisonConstraint<V>
extends CheckConstraint<V>
    This class provides base implementation of the CheckConstraint that applies binary comparison operator to a value and other property.
    Author:
    Fox Mulder
